channel.title: OverloadX - Classpath
channel.description:
Hey.
I have been trying to run a server for ages now, but i couldn't log-in on my own server. I was wondering how, and a mate told me it's cause of my classpath or something. I had to change it. I'm running on a Windows 7, can anyone tell me wether he was correct? And also, if he was correct, could u teamview with me? Would really help me out.
Add on MSN if you can help me: Taurushelp@live.be
